          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Generate variates from a multivariate hypergeometric distribution."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "The multivariate hypergeometric distribution is a generalization\nof the hypergeometric distribution."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Choose "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "nsample"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " items at random without replacement from a\ncollection with "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "N"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " distinct types.  "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "N"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " is the length of\n"
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "colors"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": ", and the values in "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "colors"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " are the number of occurrences\nof that type in the collection.  The total number of items in the\ncollection is "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "sum(colors)"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": ".  Each random variate generated by this\nfunction is a vector of length "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "N"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " holding the counts of the\ndifferent types that occurred in the "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "nsample"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " items."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "The name "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "colors"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " comes from a common description of the\ndistribution: it is the probability distribution of the number of\nmarbles of each color selected without replacement from an urn\ncontaining marbles of different colors; "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "colors[i]"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " is the number\nof marbles in the urn with color "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "i"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Extended Summary"
    },
